      "subject": "Re: Question about useEffect cleanup",
      "content": "Great question! You need cleanup when your effect sets up subscriptions, event listeners, or async operations that should be cancelled. Common examples: API calls (abort), WebSocket connections (close), or setTimeout (clear).",
